3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses learning features from selective pairs of images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is possible as the paper deals with a dataset of webcams from different places. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper applies the proposed approach to existing subtle attribute recognition problems.
